comments: Booker (PHX) is already in Lillard's (POR) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Whiteside (POR) is already in Oubre Jr.'s (PHX) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Ayton (PHX) legally contests Lillard's (POR) driving shot attempt.
Oubre Jr. (PHX) makes marginal contact with Whiteside (POR) during rebounding.
Whiteside (POR) makes marginal contact with Bridges (PHX) as both players reach for the rebound.
Oubre Jr. (PHX) extends his arm forward and makes contact to the ball and simultaneous marginal contact to Whiteside's (POR) shoulder.
Bridges (PHX) jumps into Lillard's (POR) body and affects his shot near the rim.
Ayton (PHX) is already in Bazemore's (POR) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Bazemore (POR) is already in Oubre Jr.'s (PHX) path when contact occurs and he absorbs the contact.
Booker (PHX) jumps A to B into Lillard (POR) and affects his driving shot attempt.
Lillard (POR) enters the lane prior to the ball making contact with the rim.  Booker (PHX) also enters the arc prior to Lillard (POR) releasing his dribble.
Rubio (PHX) makes marginal contact with Lillard (POR) during rebounding.

Oubre Jr. (PHX) extends his foot outside the frame of his body and makes foot to foot contact with Whiteside (POR) after he has released his shot attempt.  The contact affects Whiteside's ability to land safely.
Carter (PHX) makes marginal contact with Lillard (POR) as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Lillard (POR) places his hand momentarily on Johnson's (PHX) hip before correcting.
Simons (POR) does not establish a legal guarding position in Booker's (PHX) path prior to contact.
Anthony (POR) cleanly dislodges the ball from Johnson (PHX).  Additionally, a timeout is called by Phoenix prior to the tie up by Anthony.
Bazemore (POR) commits the take foul on Booker (PHX).
Ayton (PHX) legally contests Lillard's (POR) jump shot attempt.
Booker (PHX) advances the ball into the frontcourt within eight seconds.
